<span id="freeTextContainer11741429549313351618">Who hasn&apos;t had this sort of a day? For Alexander, it starts out bad and just gets worse and worse.<br/><br/>A great book to share with a kid who gets frustrated when &apos;everything seems to go wrong for me!&apos;<br/><br/>I love the illustrations in this, the simple situations gone bad, and Alexander&apos;s very real reactions to them.</span>
  <span id="freeText11741429549313351618" style="display:none">Who hasn't had this sort of a day? For Alexander, it starts out bad and just gets worse and worse.<br /><br />A great book to share with a kid who gets frustrated when 'everything seems to go wrong for me!'<br /><br />I love the illustrations in this, the simple situations gone bad, and Alexander's very real reactions to them.</span>
